  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/3cf76999e974857a0d94ee5830ccaa47.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=172 /></span><br>RAID. SCAVENGE. ESCAPE.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever dreamed of rummaging through dusty <strong>bunkers</strong> filled with questionable air, hungry <strong>mutants</strong>, and half-clothed <strong>survivors</strong> who desperately want your last can of beans? Then welcome to <strong>Raiders of the Apocalypse</strong>, where <strong>oxygen</strong> is precious, common sense is overrated, and every trip is a frantic race against that ticking watch on your wrist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/66d8807433c0f36e916805f1bb06752c.poster.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/66d8807433c0f36e916805f1bb06752c.webm?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/66d8807433c0f36e916805f1bb06752c.mp4?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCAVENGE & SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suit up and explore <strong>procedurally generated floors</strong> in singleplayer or team up with friends. Pry open locked rooms in search of <strong>supplies</strong>, <strong>weapons</strong>, and the occasional terrified stranger. Tread carefully—hostile <strong>mutants</strong> lurk in the corridors, ready to make you question your life choices. Hurry back before your oxygen gauge dips too low… or things get messy fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/a1ced23f6bf1ef0c9a2fb8b43f5444e6.poster.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/a1ced23f6bf1ef0c9a2fb8b43f5444e6.webm?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/a1ced23f6bf1ef0c9a2fb8b43f5444e6.mp4?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR HOME BUNKER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand</strong> and improve your own bunker between <strong>expeditions</strong>. Smash down walls, clear the rubble, and build up your space to store your ever-growing <strong>stash</strong> of loot. Invest your hard-won <strong>Recyclable Materials</strong> at the worktable to <strong>reproduce</strong> valuable <strong>gear</strong>, then pop a floppy disk into the PC to set your <strong>next destination</strong>—going deeper means bigger risks, but the rewards might just be worth it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/6f9214d89d3bb8eb43e72f650bd7ff28.poster.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/6f9214d89d3bb8eb43e72f650bd7ff28.webm?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/6f9214d89d3bb8eb43e72f650bd7ff28.mp4?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WANT MORE? FIND IT IN THE RUINS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you go, the better the <strong>loot</strong>—and the bigger the <strong>danger</strong>. With each descent, you’ll face darker halls, more cunning foes, and cryptic <strong>clues</strong> about the broken world you call home. So grab your sledgehammer, pack enough snacks, and pray that your flashlight doesn’t go out at the worst possible moment. <strong>Good luck out there!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/3cf76999e974857a0d94ee5830ccaa47.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=172 /></span><br>RAID. SCAVENGE. ESCAPE.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever dreamed of rummaging through dusty <strong>bunkers</strong> filled with questionable air, hungry <strong>mutants</strong>, and half-clothed <strong>survivors</strong> who desperately want your last can of beans? Then welcome to <strong>Raiders of the Apocalypse</strong>, where <strong>oxygen</strong> is precious, common sense is overrated, and every trip is a frantic race against that ticking watch on your wrist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/66d8807433c0f36e916805f1bb06752c.poster.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/66d8807433c0f36e916805f1bb06752c.webm?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/66d8807433c0f36e916805f1bb06752c.mp4?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCAVENGE & SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suit up and explore <strong>procedurally generated floors</strong> in singleplayer or team up with friends. Pry open locked rooms in search of <strong>supplies</strong>, <strong>weapons</strong>, and the occasional terrified stranger. Tread carefully—hostile <strong>mutants</strong> lurk in the corridors, ready to make you question your life choices. Hurry back before your oxygen gauge dips too low… or things get messy fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/a1ced23f6bf1ef0c9a2fb8b43f5444e6.poster.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/a1ced23f6bf1ef0c9a2fb8b43f5444e6.webm?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/a1ced23f6bf1ef0c9a2fb8b43f5444e6.mp4?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR HOME BUNKER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand</strong> and improve your own bunker between <strong>expeditions</strong>. Smash down walls, clear the rubble, and build up your space to store your ever-growing <strong>stash</strong> of loot. Invest your hard-won <strong>Recyclable Materials</strong> at the worktable to <strong>reproduce</strong> valuable <strong>gear</strong>, then pop a floppy disk into the PC to set your <strong>next destination</strong>—going deeper means bigger risks, but the rewards might just be worth it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/6f9214d89d3bb8eb43e72f650bd7ff28.poster.avif?t=1748534086\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/6f9214d89d3bb8eb43e72f650bd7ff28.webm?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3504460/extras/6f9214d89d3bb8eb43e72f650bd7ff28.mp4?t=1748534086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WANT MORE? FIND IT IN THE RUINS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you go, the better the <strong>loot</strong>—and the bigger the <strong>danger</strong>. With each descent, you’ll face darker halls, more cunning foes, and cryptic <strong>clues</strong> about the broken world you call home. So grab your sledgehammer, pack enough snacks, and pray that your flashlight doesn’t go out at the worst possible moment. <strong>Good luck out there!</strong></p>",
